{"tid":1659291,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"BMW 2 Series Gran Coupe","createTime":"2019-10-17T01:08:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T05:22:43.000Z","uid":236926,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"39121d5e8d82934891db8ef366a352e1e7186259","tid":1659291,"uid":236926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T01:08:29.000Z","msg":"你以為佢會用coupe後驅，又會有直六Turbo版？<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">WRONG</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HUeOUBk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHUeOUBk.jpg&h=e462f52c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N1BaojX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN1BaojX.jpg&h=2713fe20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5JAixeh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5JAixeh.jpg&h=8d228027&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n沿用新一代1 Series, X1, X2的UKL前驅底盤及1 Series的全線引擎 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aZnQome.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaZnQome.jpg&h=1a21a1f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/75PfzsV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F75PfzsV.jpg&h=bee512e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JFVKsNW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJFVKsNW.jpg&h=a9baaa52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mOOTk7X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmOOTk7X.jpg&h=9b6033fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n此部作為Mercedes Benz CLA的同級車款分別有1.5三缸渦輪218i，柴油220d及2.0四缸Turbo的 M235i<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">218i</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UyXQomx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUyXQomx.jpg&h=ba45fa79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GozZ08d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGozZ08d.jpg&h=a59e4404&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F7TDxeU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF7TDxeU.jpg&h=218f14d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬力達138匹，162lb-ft 扭力可選配xDrive，波箱可選六速棍波或七速自動波<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">M235i</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FVFB3mP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFVFB3mP.jpg&h=6f1efe03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YkOW3mQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYkOW3mQ.jpg&h=91cfa94e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GW8Tk8v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGW8Tk8v.jpg&h=09a033c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dbbNqAb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdbbNqAb.jpg&h=ac9b45a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬力達302匹，，332lb-ft扭力，標配xDrive及只有八速自動波箱，更比218i多出前LSD, M Sport 煞車，避震, 18吋合金軨 及車身内外的M部件 <br />\nCar and Driver雜誌測試M235i原型車0至100km/h (60mph)加速為4.6秒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L17XNWg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL17XNWg.jpg&h=0abfb74a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uLgQ7Wk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuLgQ7Wk.jpg&h=e822cfd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hvjCNOS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhvjCNOS.jpg&h=271572f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pDGNqAy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpDGNqAy.jpg&h=615de36f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n車身比1 Series長 200mm ，所以後座腳部空間更多，多出33mm及更多頭部空間<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8kdsqAC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8kdsqAC.jpg&h=1fefd4ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NRrBiVD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNRrBiVD.jpg&h=7172f087&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而因有尾箱的關係，Gran Coupe會多出 430 公升的儲物空間 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BRj7qzc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBRj7qzc.jpg&h=7de9dffd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gfKjgFT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgfKjgFT.jpg&h=aeedd148&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ysva7Nz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fysva7Nz.jpg&h=ed7b49f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nM Performance 部件仕樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ni19DNt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNi19DNt.jpg&h=234a29c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PvsXNFP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPvsXNFP.jpg&h=81d00d21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u952YNv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu952YNv.jpg&h=7e7cd0fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HVEGuUb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHVEGuUb.jpg&h=63e9941c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國預售價為&pound;25,816<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過公平啲，早少少出的M8 Coupe, Convertible同埋8系Gran Coupe型好多，放啲相中和翻下對眼同心理<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4cpCNU8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4cpCNU8.jpg&h=d1834c1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mBARSmP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmBARSmP.jpg&h=9275584e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x3bQ7Va.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx3bQ7Va.jpg&h=dc4469a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wXmd5GR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwXmd5GR.jpg&h=fc4f1214&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OLQuD1S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOLQuD1S.jpg&h=38bdb033&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qB4SBOy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqB4SBOy.jpg&h=2107e5a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JLh5cmU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJLh5cmU.jpg&h=1c5e6868&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/45D4sVf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F45D4sVf.jpg&h=5cf63a01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gpt0LGW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGpt0LGW.jpg&h=a58e17c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M6WQ7Vh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM6WQ7Vh.jpg&h=7ddbaa54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMC1u8L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMC1u8L.jpg&h=0a01e597&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zj52Y16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzj52Y16.jpg&h=9a2ff15e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BYEWi17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBYEWi17.jpg&h=19831315&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qwWd5G8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqwWd5G8.jpg&h=2fb6a574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZjHT5G9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg